short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export a LinkedIn profile to PDF

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Turn your LinkedIn profile into a resume in minutes.

Steps:
1. Install ResumeBoostAI Chrome Extension
2. Go to your LinkedIn Profile
3. Activate extension and click on Download PDF
4. Once you download your PDF,  go to https://resumeboostai.com/resume-import
5. Drop PDF and click on Upload Resume
6. Check information and edit resume if needed
7. Click on Download Resume

Voila! now you can land your dream job 

Check out the best AI resume builder: https://resumeboostai.com/
